rows.label: tev065801_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_SEL0011
rows.name:
Ask Zo Zinath about the Wrothians'
decision to leave the Ganglion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Zo Zinath if anything is troubling him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Zo Zinath if anything is troubling him.

rows.label: tev065801_SEL2021
rows.name: Ask Zo Zinath about recent developments.

rows.label: tev065801_SEL2031
rows.name: Ask Zo Zinath what he will do next.

rows.label: tev065801_SEL2041
rows.name: Ask Zo Zinath about recent developments.

rows.label: tev065801_MSG0001
rows.name:
The finest decision Prince Jiarg has ever made!
It lifted the dark clouds on my heart.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG0002
rows.name:
We had nothing and they had everything,
so we acquiesced to their putrid wishes...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG0003
rows.name:
But the valor and strength of the fierce Wrothians was
never meant to serve feckless cowards like them!
Long did we struggle with the shame of it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG0004
rows.name:
Now that we are free, we must fend for ourselves,
to be sure. But we still know how to fight.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG0005
rows.name:
We will use these talents to feed our people just as
our people did before this all began.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG0010
rows.name:
Our spies report suspicious activity in a fortress of
Sylvalum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG0011
rows.name:
Had we resources, we would deal with it forthwithâ€”
but it seems we want for everything these days.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG0012
rows.name:
Ah! Forget I spoke. This was not a matter to bring
before strangers.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG1001
rows.name:
Thanks to the relief supplies you sent us,
we draw ever closer to combat readiness.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG1002
rows.name:
We will not remain on the defensive. Once ready,
we intend to strike first.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG1003
rows.name:
Our spies report suspicious activity in a fortress of
Sylvalum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG1004
rows.name:
Gi Nogan will go there first to secure the perimeter,
then we intend send in our raiders. But do we have
enough of them...?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG2001
rows.name: We are still trying to make sense of that schematic.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG2002
rows.name:
It appears to be a high-output Skell weapon with range
and power beyond anything we have seen before.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG2003
rows.name:
Even if we did craft it, is there a Skell in existence
capable of wielding it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG2004
rows.name: If the Ganglion already have such a Skell, then...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG2005
rows.name:
Well, we must be ready for anything. Let us keep our
wits about us before going into battle from now on.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG2010
rows.name:
One day I would like to build an impregnable castle
here like the one we had on our homeworld.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG2011
rows.name: It would be just as magnificent as your city of New LA.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG2012
rows.name:
Then let us see the Ganglion throw their might at us!
We would sneer as they turned tail and fled.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG2013
rows.name: I cannot pursue this dream now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG2014
rows.name:
But time changes much, and if I am patient,
the key to building my castle will present itself.
I must hold fast to the dream![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG2019
rows.name:
It is purely conjecture, but I believe I know the nature
of weapon this schematic describes.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG2020
rows.name:
It is a high-output weapon designed specifically for the
mech that Luxaar was using.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG2021
rows.name:
No other piece of machinery could possibly wield
something this formidable.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG2022
rows.name:
We were lucky to destroy Luxaar before he could
complete the weapon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065801_MSG2023
rows.name:
It would have been an implement of death in his hands.
Even you might not have emerged victorious.[ST:wait ]
